qMetaDef.description: Overview sheet providing a "snapshot" view of license usage.
qMetaDef.title: Usage Snapshot

qDef.qDef:
IF(license_type_enabled<>'Token-based',
Num(Count({<[Access Type]={"Professional"},proxy_session_id_app_id={"*"}>} distinct UserId),'#,##0'),
Num(Count({<[Access Type]={"User"},proxy_session_id_app_id={"*"}>} distinct UserId),'#,##0')
)

=IF(license_type_enabled<>'Token-based',
Num(Count({<[Access Type]={"Analyzer"},proxy_session_id_app_id={"*"}>} distinct UserId),'#,##0'),
num(ceil(count({<[Access Type]={'Login'}>} distinct UsageId)/10),'#,##0')
)

qStringExpression.qExpr:
=IF(license_type_enabled<>'Token-based' 
	AND [License Allocated Analyzer Capacity (Minutes)]>0
    AND Not Sum([Analyzer Capacity Used (Minutes)])>0,
    '* Analyzer Capacity Minutes usage is captured historically in the logs starting in June 2019 Sense.' &
    ' Earlier versions of Sense will report Analyzer Capacity Minutes = 0 in this chart even though minutes were used historically.'
    ,'')

qDef.qDef:
IF(license_type_enabled<>'Token-based',
Num(Count({<[Access Type]={"Professional"},proxy_session_id_app_id={"*"},last_month={'1'}>} distinct UserId),'#,##0'),
Num(Count({<[Access Type]={"User"},proxy_session_id_app_id={"*"},last_month={'1'}>} distinct UserId),'#,##0')
)

=IF(license_type_enabled<>'Token-based',
Num(Count({<[Access Type]={"Analyzer"},proxy_session_id_app_id={"*"},last_month={'1'}>} distinct UserId),'#,##0'),
num(ceil(count({<[Access Type]={'Login'},last_month={'1'}>} distinct UsageId)/10),'#,##0')
)
Num(Sum({<[Access Type]={"Analyzer Capacity"}, last_month = {'1'}>} [Analyzer Capacity Used (Minutes)]),'#,##0')

qMsg.qv: No Analyzer Capacity Minutes Used for current selections.

customErrorMessage.calcCond: No Analyzer Capacity Minutes Used for current selections.

qDef.qDef:
='Sense: ' & EngineVer 
& ' (' & Concat({<[Unified Licensing Product]={"Sense"}>} Distinct Hostname,',') & ') '
& If(qlikview_license_logs_present=1,'; Qlikview: ' & qlikview_maxstring_exe_version
	& ' (' & Concat({<[Unified Licensing Product]={"Qlikview"}>} Distinct Hostname,',') & ') '
    )

IF((license_type_enabled)='Token-based','Not Licensed',
    'licensed = ' & Num(Sum({<[License Token Type]={"Professional*"}>}[License Total Tokens]),'#,##0') 
    & ', unallocated = ' & Num(Sum({<[License Token Type]={"Professional*"}>}[License Total Tokens]-[License Allocated Tokens]),'#,##0')
    & ', allocated = ' & Num(Sum({<[License Token Type]={"Professional*"}>}[License Allocated Tokens]),'#,##0')

    & ', allocated but unused = ' & Num(Sum({<[License Token Type]={"Professional*"}>}[License Allocated Tokens]-[License Used Tokens]),'#,##0')
    )

qStringExpression.qExpr: IF((license_type_enabled)='Token-based','% of Login Access available','% of unallocated Analyzer Access')

qDef.qDef:
IF((license_type_enabled)='Token-based','Not Licensed',
    'licensed = ' & Num(Sum({<[License Token Type]={"Analyzer Capacity"}>} [License Allocated Analyzer Capacity (Minutes)]),'#,##0') 
    & ', used = ' & Num(Sum({<[License Token Type]={"Analyzer Capacity"}>} [License Used Analyzer Capacity (Minutes)]),'#,##0')
    & ', available = ' &  Num(Sum({<[License Token Type]={"Analyzer Capacity"}>} [License Allocated Analyzer Capacity (Minutes)])
    		- Sum({<[License Token Type]={"Analyzer Capacity"}>} [License Unavailable Analyzer Capacity (Minutes)])
            - Sum({<[License Token Type]={"Analyzer Capacity"}>} [License Used Analyzer Capacity (Minutes)])
            ,'#,##0')
    )

qStringExpression.qExpr:
'The total Analyzer Capacity minutes subscribed to for each month. '
& IF([License Allocated Analyzer Capacity (Minutes)]>5,
	chr(10) & ' To date in '& MonthName(Today(1)) & ' you have used ' & Num([License Used Analyzer Capacity (Minutes)],'#,##0') 
    & ' of ' & Num([License Allocated Analyzer Capacity (Minutes)],'#,##0') 
    & ' total minutes as reported at ' & ReloadTime() & '.'
& chr(10) & ' At an average of ' & Num([License Used Analyzer Capacity (Minutes)]/(today(1)-MonthStart(Today(1))),'#,##0') & ' minutes used per day, you would ' 
& IF([License Used Analyzer Capacity (Minutes)]/(today(1)-MonthStart(Today(1)))>5,'run out of minutes in ' & Num(CEIL([License Allocated Analyzer Capacity (Minutes)]/([License Used Analyzer Capacity (Minutes)]/(today(1)-MonthStart(Today(1))))),'#,##0') & ' days.',' never run out!')
& chr(10) & chr(10) & 'Analyzer Capacity minutes reset the first day of each calendar month. '
,' ')
& ' Refer to the online help documentation: https://help.qlik.com/en-US/search/?q=analyzer+capacity+license'

qDef.qDef:
IF((license_type_enabled)<>'Token-based','not licensed',
    'Total Tokens in License = ' & Num(Sum([License Total Tokens]),'#,##0') 
    & '; allocated = ' & Num(Sum({<[License Token Type]={"User Access"}>}[License Allocated Tokens]),'#,##0')
    & ', used = ' & Num(Sum({<[License Token Type]={"User Access"}>}[License Used Tokens]),'#,##0')
    & ', allocated but unused = ' & Num(Sum({<[License Token Type]={"User Access"}>}[License Allocated Tokens]-[License Used Tokens]),'#,##0')
    )

IF((license_type_enabled)<>'Token-based','not licensed',
     ' allocated = ' & Num(Sum({<[License Token Type]={"Login Access"}>}[License Allocated Tokens]),'#,##0')
    & ', used = ' & Num(Sum({<[License Token Type]={"Login Access"}>}[License Used Tokens]),'#,##0')
    & ', allocated but unused = ' & Num(Sum({<[License Token Type]={"Login Access"}>}[License Allocated Tokens]-[License Used Tokens]),'#,##0')
    )
